{
  "title": "Resources for ReFi 101 📚 | Roundup #51",
  "slug": "refi-roundup-51",
  "html": "<p><em>Greetings, fellow regens! I'm <a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xPhaedrus\">Phaedrus</a>, contributor at <a href=\"https://www.klimadao.finance/\">KlimaDAO</a> and the <a href=\"anchor.fm/refipodcast\">ReFi Podcast</a>, and host of the <a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/potk/\">Planet of the Klimates podcast</a>. I'm honoured to have been invited to share my perspective on ReFi this week through another ReFi Roundup!</em></p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-19.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/02/image-19.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-19.png 768w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Source: Stable Difussion</figcaption></figure><h1 id=\"where-to-start-in-refi-%F0%9F%A4%94\">Where to start in ReFi? 🤔</h1><p>Most of us have heard this question before. Yet whether it's a regen-curious degen, a sustainability professional interested in blockchain, or just an interested friend, it can be challenging for newbies to learn the basics and find their place.</p><p>Maybe your just getting started yourself, or maybe you want to share the word with friends and colleagues, here are some new resources that popped up this week👇🏽</p><h3 id=\"beggining-down-the-rabbit-hole-%F0%9F%95%B3%EF%B8%8F-%F0%9F%90%87\">Beggining down the rabbit hole 🕳️ 🐇</h3><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/boydcohen\">Boyd Cohen</a> from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/IoMob_net\">IoMob</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/wheelcoin\">Wheelcoin</a> created a quick-fire guide on some of the essential resources and starting points for anyone looking to get into ReFi: \"<a href=\"https://boydcohen.medium.com/going-down-the-refi-rabbit-hole-5fa9c5960b10\">Going down the ReFi Rabbit Hole</a>\".</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">After my personal <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> week in review tweet <a href=\"https://twitter.com/kierwhite?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@kierwhite</a> mentioned the utility of having a starter list for newbies.<br><br>So I quickly put this together highlighting:<br>1) major ReFi orgs <br>2) ReFi podcasts<br>3) ReFi venture funds<br>4) Protocols<br>5) People to follow<a href=\"https://t.co/Hcf3A28atp\">https://t.co/Hcf3A28atp</a></p>&mdash; Boyd Cohen ◘ (@boydcohen) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/boydcohen/status/1624044195596967938?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 10, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://boydcohen.medium.com/going-down-the-refi-rabbit-hole-5fa9c5960b10\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read article</a></div><h3 id=\"refi-glossary-entry-%F0%9F%93%97\">ReFi Glossary Entry 📗</h3><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/owocki\">Kevin Owocki</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/emiyazono\">Evan Miyazono</a> launched a <a href=\"https://coinmarketcap.com/alexandria/glossary/regenerative-finance-refi\">ReFi glossary entry at Coinmarketcap</a> providing a great starting point for definitions and explorations into the major impact areas of ReFi. You can also check out Kevin's <a href=\"https://store.gitcoin.co/products/green-pill-book-digital-edition\">Greenpill </a>book for deeper reading and insight.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">ReFi definition is now in coinmarketcap! <br><br>/ht <a href=\"https://twitter.com/YAPGlobalTeam?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@YAPGlobalTeam</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/emiyazono?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@emiyazono</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/4ruufnyVo5\">https://t.co/4ruufnyVo5</a></p>&mdash; KΞV.eth (🤖,💚) (@owocki) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/owocki/status/1622993422452928513?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 7, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://coinmarketcap.com/alexandria/glossary/regenerative-finance-refi\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">View glossary</a></div><h3 id=\"blockdatas-definition-and-market-map-%F0%9F%A7%AD\">Blockdata's definition and market map 🧭</h3><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/blockdata_tech\">Blockdata</a> - an organisations providing tools and insights to accelerate enterprise blockchain adoption provided their answer to the question of <a href=\"https://www.blockdata.tech/blog/general/what-is-regenerative-finance\">What Is Regenerative Finance?</a>. They also created their version of a ReFi market map based on use cases with 22 organisations from in the sector 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-18.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1345\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/02/image-18.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/02/image-18.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/02/image-18.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-18.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.blockdata.tech/blog/general/what-is-regenerative-finance\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read article</a></div><h3 id=\"klima-dao-webinar-series-%F0%9F%93%BA\">Klima DAO webinar series 📺</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.klimadao.finance/\">KlimaDAO</a> launched their new 'On Set' webinar series this past Tuesday. The first event focused on the fundamentals of digital carbon and was designed to appeal to as broad of an audience as possible. With over 850 sign-ups across the ReFi and blockchain worlds, as well as key academic and voluntary carbon market players, it's fair to say there is a strong appetite for accelerating climate action with the tools that web3 provides.</p><p>Registrations included representatives from 67 different countries, and it was interesting to see the majority of attendees had <em>not</em> interacted with the digital carbon market in any way before. ReFi is far more than echo chamber of familiar faces, we're thriving and reaching an ever-growing audience looking to make an impact.</p><p>Check out this <a href=\"https://twitter.com/KlimaDAO/status/1623666568952713217?s=20&amp;t=_MO_R9XasT7djR3kxbx85A\">Twitter thread</a> to replay the webinar, dive into some of the key observations made during the event, as well as register for '<a href=\"klima.fyi/onset-2\">On Set</a>' part 2! </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Missed out on Tuesday?<br>Watch the first ON SET webinar recording!<br><br>▶️ <a href=\"https://t.co/lu8lzwSTFg\">https://t.co/lu8lzwSTFg</a><br><br>With 850 sign-ups and 260 attendees live with us ON SET, the Fundamentals of Digital Carbon webinar was a huge success and a great start to the 3-part series.<br><br>Some takeaways below:<br>1/4 <a href=\"https://t.co/XknD88o9rJ\">pic.twitter.com/XknD88o9rJ</a></p>&mdash; KlimaDAO (@KlimaDAO) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/KlimaDAO/status/1623666568952713217?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 9, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"klima.fyi/onset-2\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Register for On Set #2!</a></div><h3 id=\"sharing-is-caring-%F0%9F%94%88\">Sharing is caring 🔈</h3><p>There is always room for more regens in the community. The more people are aligned with the ReFi movement, the more impact we can create as a whole. LFShareeee 🗣️ </p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://ctt.ac/irWQc\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Share Now!</a></div><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/02/ReFi-Cover.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/02/ReFi-Cover.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"%F0%9F%94%A5-projects-of-the-week\">🔥 Projects of the Week</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"ema-showcase-of-top-voted-projects-from-the-refi-dao-websiteem\"><em>A showcase of top voted projects from the ReFi DAO website!</em></h3><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/projects\" class=\"kg-header-card-button\">View More</a></div><p>Here were the top 5 most voted projects of the week at <a href=\"refidao.com\">refidao.com</a>:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/ReFiDAO.com-Refi-Projects-of-the-Week--6th-13thFeb-2023-.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1123\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/02/ReFiDAO.com-Refi-Projects-of-the-Week--6th-13thFeb-2023-.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/02/ReFiDAO.com-Refi-Projects-of-the-Week--6th-13thFeb-2023-.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/02/ReFiDAO.com-Refi-Projects-of-the-Week--6th-13thFeb-2023-.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w2400/2023/02/ReFiDAO.com-Refi-Projects-of-the-Week--6th-13thFeb-2023-.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"></figure><ol><li>🐰 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/stiamee\"><strong>Follow The Black Hare</strong></a>: a cyberpunk-themed RPG adventure with multiple endings.</li><li>️🧑🏾‍🤝‍🧑🏿 <a href=\"https://www.kolektivo.network/\"><strong>Kolektivo</strong></a>: enabling local communities to create and manage their own regenerative economy to fuel prosperity.</li><li>🫶 <a href=\"https://giveth.io/\"><strong>Giveth</strong></a>: a decentralized Altruistic Community using blockchain technology to make the world a better place.</li><li>🐑 <a href=\"https://traditionaldreamfactory.com/\"><strong>Traditional Dream Factory</strong></a>: a regenerative village in Alentejo, Portugal prototyping a land DAO model to steward the planet.</li><li>🏰 <a href=\"https://www.atlantians.world/\"><strong>Atlantis</strong></a>: a global squad of changemakers  for social and climate impact and a platform to build reputation.</li></ol><p><strong>Votes have now been reset</strong> so head over to <a href=\"refidao.com\">refidao.com</a>, make an account, and show some support to your favourite projects in the ecosystem this week! 💚</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/projects\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Vote away!</a></div><hr><h3 id=\"add-your-refi-project-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Add your ReFi Project! 👇🏽</h3><p><em>Have a project you want to add to our database? Click the button below to submit an application!</em></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/submit-project\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Submit project</a></div><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-6.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-6.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-podcasts-%F0%9F%8E%99%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi Podcasts 🎙️</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emtop-audio-and-video-content-from-creators-across-the-web-em%F0%9F%98%8A\"><em>Top audio and video content from creators across the web </em>😊</h3></div><h2 id=\"refi-podcast\">ReFi Podcast</h2><p><a href=\"https://anchor.fm/refipodcast\">ReFi Podcast</a> dropped a fresh episode for listeners this week, exploring sustainable infrastructure funding with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tx_shep\">Ben Sheppard</a> from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/silta_fi\">Silta Finance</a>. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">&quot;How might we redirect the INSANE sums of DeFi capital to where it&#39;s needed most?&quot;<br><br>In this week&#39;s episode with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tx_shep?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@tx_shep</a> from <a href=\"https://twitter.com/silta_fi?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@silta_fi</a> we hear about their due diligence protocol &amp; the  opportunity of infrastructure financing<br><br>🎥 <a href=\"https://t.co/UmnLZ32bY3\">https://t.co/UmnLZ32bY3</a><br>🎧 <a href=\"https://t.co/qU6MR9T5o7\">https://t.co/qU6MR9T5o7</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/d6adzpI0uj\">pic.twitter.com/d6adzpI0uj</a></p>&mdash; ReFi Podcast (@ReFiPodcast) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiPodcast/status/1623281765212164097?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 8, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><p><a href=\"https://anchor.fm/refipodcast/episodes/Financing-Sustainable-Infrastructure-with-Ben-from-Silta-Finance-e1ui2vd\">Listen to the full episode directly</a> or watch the conversation over <a href=\"https://youtu.be/cw22rBW4gFE\">on YouTube</a>.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cw22rBW4gFE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"ReFi Podcast BONUS EPISODE: Financing Sustainable Infrastructure with Ben from Silta Finance\"></iframe></figure><h2 id=\"the-network-state-podcast\">The Network State Podcast</h2><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/balajis\">Balaji</a> just <a href=\"https://twitter.com/balajis/status/1623189534757498886\">launched the 'Network State' podcast episode #1</a> featuring none other than <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VitalikButerin\">Vitalik Buterin</a> himself.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Introducing the Network State Podcast.<br><br>The first episode features me and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VitalikButerin?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@VitalikButerin</a>. We talk about starting new countries, upgrading Ethereum, and improving yourself! <a href=\"https://t.co/HnsYCbFBVU\">pic.twitter.com/HnsYCbFBVU</a></p>&mdash; Balaji (@balajis) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/balajis/status/1623189534757498886?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 8, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"planetary-regeneration\">Planetary Regeneration</h2><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/RRansil\">Red Ransil</a> sat down with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gregory_landua\">Gregory Landua</a> on <a href=\"https://www.regen.network/\">Regen Network</a>'s Planetary Regeneration Podcast, to discuss the voluntary carbon market, carbon accounting methodologies, and building a climate-positive informational infrastructure for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/web3?src=hashtag_click\">#web3</a> with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/filecoingreen\">@filecoingreen</a>:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">📢NEW PODCAST<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gregory_landua?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@gregory_landua</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RRansil?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@rransil</a> of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/filecoingreen?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@filecoingreen</a> cover how <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/web3?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#web3</a> is helping to:<br><br>👉Create rigorous and verifiable <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/carboncredit?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#carboncredit</a> markets<br>👉Accelerate decarbonization<br>👉Inform offset purchasing decisions<br>👉Incentivize <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> activity<br><br>🎧<a href=\"https://t.co/QVXKALi1Ys\">https://t.co/QVXKALi1Ys</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/emsV4B1Hia\">pic.twitter.com/emsV4B1Hia</a></p>&mdash; Regen Network (@regen_network) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/regen_network/status/1622690032703373312?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 6, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"other-%F0%9F%94%A5-podcasts-on-our-radar\">Other 🔥 Podcasts on our Radar:</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/VinceFHorn\">Vince Horn</a> talks about Decentralizing Dharma on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/owocki\">Kevin Owocki</a>'s <a href=\"https://newsletter.banklesshq.com/p/decentralized-dharma-with-vince-horn\">Green Pill Podcast #86 </a></li><li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/timrann\">Tim Rann</a> of <a href=\"https://anchor.fm/theownershipeconomy/episodes/Episode-050---From-MFi-to-ReFi-Impact-Investment-Insights-and-Possibilities--with-Tim-Rann-of-Mercy-Corps-Ventures-e1uoenf\">Mercy Corps Ventures on The Ownership Economy podcast episode #50</a>.</li><li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/NiharNeelakanti\">Nihar Neelakanti</a> of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ecosapiensxyz\">Ecosapiens</a> on <a href=\"https://www.cryptoaltruism.org/blog/crypto-altruism-podcast-episode89-ecosapiens-merging-climate-tech-and-digital-assets-with-the-first-carbon-backed-nft\">the Crypto Altruism podcast #89</a>.</li><li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/climateXcrypto\">John Elisson</a> on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thegrifft\">Griff Green</a>'s <a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/broadcasts/1BRJjZVlwWoJw\">GM! podcast #5</a>.</li></ul><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-newsbites-%F0%9F%97%9E%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi NewsBites 🗞️</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emthe-latest-updates-across-refi-twitter-and-beyondem\"><em>The latest updates across ReFi Twitter and beyond...</em></h3></div><h2 id=\"thallos-launched-two-way-bridge-%F0%9F%8C%89\">Thallo's Launched Two-Way Bridge 🌉 </h2><p>ReFi player <a href=\"https://www.thallo.io/\">Thallo</a> has just launched a two-way bridge, working with carbon credits from the <a href=\"https://puro.earth/\">Puro.earth</a> registry:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">🚨 It&#39;s official: we&#39;ve brought the first carbon credits onto the blockchain through our two-way bridge! 🧵<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/worldfirst?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#worldfirst</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/tokenization?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#tokenization</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/carboncredits?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#carboncredits</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/381yZqHujo\">pic.twitter.com/381yZqHujo</a></p>&mdash; Thallo (@thallo_io) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thallo_io/status/1624044537344565249?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 10, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"icymi-refis-tree-planting-world-champ-%F0%9F%8E%89\">ICYMI: ReFi's Tree-Planting World Champ! 🎉</h2><p>This one has roots that go back just a bit further than one week, but recently ReFi community member and marathon Twitter Spaces host <a href=\"https://twitter.com/JimiCohen\">Jimi Cohen (Treegen)</a> apparently broke a tree-planting world record - with 25,650 mangrove propagules planted in just under one day! 👀 </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">WE DID IT!!! 🌳 I broke the world record for Most Trees Planted in 24 Hours &amp; have been dubbed the Tree Planting World Champion!! 🎉<br><br>It was a STRUGGLE, but so worth it!<br><br>Check out the 🧵to learn about the to 6 challenges &amp; find out the final number planted👇 <a href=\"https://t.co/Q2EyByKZnn\">pic.twitter.com/Q2EyByKZnn</a></p>&mdash; Jimi🌳🐝 (Treegen.eth) (@JimiCohen) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/JimiCohen/status/1620026679526834178?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 30, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">GM Regens 💚<br><br>Feeling grateful for all the opportunities to make an impact that life has given me 🌳 What are you thankful for today? <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Gratitude?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Gratitude</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/ucxPMechTZ\">pic.twitter.com/ucxPMechTZ</a></p>&mdash; Jimi🌳🐝 (Treegen.eth) (@JimiCohen) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/JimiCohen/status/1623950547500863488?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 10, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"hbar-foundation-sustainable-impact-fund-%F0%9F%8E%89\">HBAR Foundation Sustainable Impact Fund! 🎉</h2><p>The <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HBAR_foundation\">HBAR Foundation</a> revealed a deep dive thread on the investment thesis behind their Sustainable Impact Fund - which is designed to fight climate change and make ReFi a reality by bringing the balance sheet of the planet to the public ledger:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">The Sustainable Impact Fund (SIF), was set up with one mission in mind: to fight climate change and bring regenerative finance (<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a>) to reality by bringing the balance sheet of the planet to the public ledger 🌍 <a href=\"https://t.co/fq5gVlOY7Q\">pic.twitter.com/fq5gVlOY7Q</a></p>&mdash; HBAR Foundation (@HBAR_foundation) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HBAR_foundation/status/1622607823535308801?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 6, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-1.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-1.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-events-%F0%9F%AA%A9\">ReFi Events 🪩</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emget-your-refi-on-with-friends-in-person-and-onlineem\"><em>Get your ReFi on with friends in-person and online...</em></h3><a href=\"https://refispring.com/\" class=\"kg-header-card-button\">View more</a></div><h1 id=\"looking-forward-%F0%9F%93%8D\">Looking Forward 📍</h1><p><em>Some of the exciting events coming up soon... Make sure to grab some tickets and support the ReFi regenerative renaissance wherever you are from! </em></p><h3 id=\"web3-x-social-impact-%F0%9F%91%90\"><a href=\"https://refisummit.org/\">Web3 x Social Impact</a> 👐</h3><p><strong>(February 14th, 2023 17.30 UTC)</strong>: A LinkedIn audio event featuring  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jasdrie\">Jasper Driessens</a> of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/glodollar\">Glo stablecoin</a>, who is working to end poverty, and <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/peacefulprogress/?originalSubdomain=in\">Utkarsh Patel</a> of <a href=\"https://solarpunkdao.earth/\">Earth coin</a>, who is dedicated to funding climate solutions.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/events/web3-socialimpact703018528733