isboa: Kick-off</a> 🎉</h3><p><strong>(February 7th, 2023, 18.00 UTC, Lisbon)</strong>: The 1st <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiLisboa\">ReFi Lisboa</a> event, with talks from leading developers, web3 founders, and social entrepreneurs.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/ReFi-Lisboa\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-16.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1160\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/02/image-16.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/02/image-16.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/02/image-16.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-16.png 2028w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://lu.ma/ReFi-Lisboa\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Register for ReFi Lisboa</a></div><p><a href=\"klima.fyi/onset-2\">KlimaDAO \"On Set\" Webinar Series #2</a> 🎪 <br><strong>(March 7, 2023, 1600 UTC)</strong>: As a follow-up to their February 7th launch event, the second in Klima's \"On Set\" series of webinars exploring the Digital Carbon Market (DCM), will bring together even more builders to explore how the fundamentals of digital carbon are being leveraged to accelerate climate finance. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">The Digital Carbon Market is evolving, and offers an unprecedented opportunity to accelerate climate finance globally.<br><br>Join ON SET #2 | Leveraging Digital Carbon to be at the forefront of the carbon market&#39;s evolution.<br><br>🗓️ 16:00 UTC, March 7th, 2023<br>👉 <a href=\"https://t.co/q3jdAUdEln\">https://t.co/q3jdAUdEln</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/q375OGXWSV\">pic.twitter.com/q375OGXWSV</a></p>&mdash; KlimaDAO (@KlimaDAO) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/KlimaDAO/status/1624105921256345600?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 10, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"klima.fyi/onset-2\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Register for KlimaDAO&#x27;s &quot;On Set&quot; #2!</a></div><h3 id=\"refi-summitmomentum-building-%E2%9A%A1\"><a href=\"https://refisummit.org/\">ReFi Summit - Momentum Building</a> ⚡</h3><p><strong>(May 24th -25th, 2023, Seattle)</strong>: <a href=\"https://refisummit.org/\">ReFi Summit</a> will return this coming May, following it's launch event last year. You can get in the loop and learn more about this year's offering from founders during a <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiSummit/status/1623349051944218624?s=20&amp;t=8bXfYHeEWnpEVqnA9DVwEQ\">live Twitter Space event coming up Friday, February 17th</a>. Set your reminder using the link in the post here:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Come and join <a href=\"https://twitter.com/rexstjohn?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@rexstjohn</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jethrollinsodom?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@jethrollinsodom</a> in conversation about the upcoming <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> Summit this May in Seattle! Friday Feb 17th at 9am PST. See you there! 🌱 <a href=\"https://t.co/WpWLSf8Bwk\">https://t.co/WpWLSf8Bwk</a></p>&mdash; ReFiSummit (@ReFiSummit) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiSummit/status/1623349051944218624?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 8, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://refisummit.org/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Register for ReFi Summit</a></div><hr><h2 id=\"add-your-refi-event-%F0%9F%91%87%F0%9F%8F%BD\">Add your ReFi event! 👇🏽</h2><p><em>Got a ReFi, crypto, or climate event coming up and w