\"></script>\n</figure><p><strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/dClimateDAO\">dClimate</a> \"<a href=\"https://blog.dclimate.net/data-refined-01/\">Data Refined</a>\" 1st edition: The Newsletter for All Things Climate Data ⛅</strong></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">1/ Please meet Data ReFined, our bi-weekly newsletter about climate data, the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ReFi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ReFi</a> movement and data-driven climate impact🌎<br><br>Read the latest edition via the link below<br>or scroll down to see some highlights 👇<a href=\"https://t.co/IUEv2zuyA8\">https://t.co/IUEv2zuyA8</a></p>&mdash; dClimate (@dClimateDAO) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/dClimateDAO/status/1624064166557360128?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 10, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-5.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-5.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"thank-you-%F0%9F%A4%A9\">Thank you! 🤩</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emfor-being-a-part-of-the-ever-evolving-movement-to-create-a-radically-better-futureem\"><em>For being a part of the ever evolving movement to create a radically better future...</em></h3></div><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-grey\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">⚫</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\"><em>\"</em><b>Those who contemplate the beauty of the earth find reserves of strength that will endure as long as life lasts</b>.” - Rachel Carson (author of 1962 book '<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Silent_Spring\">Silent Spring</a>')</div></div><p>Have a fantastic week, friends &amp; we'll see y